                  </hi>. I live at No. 44, John-street, Tottenham-court-road—I rent the house—I never saw the prisoner till last Saturday, when he was in</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="184705100049"></xptr>
               <p>custody—he never lodged at my house—I did not order any coals—I refused to take them in.</p>
